# 台大法規助理 

一個使用 RAG 技術、結合 Qwen 模型的台大法規問答系統。

Use bm25 algorithm to retrieve the top 5 relevant documents from the 台大資工相關規範, then use Qwen/Qwen1.5-7B-Chat model to answer the question based on the retrieved documents.
The relevant score depends on the content of the documents and the question asked.


